"Strive to enter in at the strait gate: for many, I say unto you, will seek to enter in, and shall not be able" (Luke 1 3:24).
I want my voice to echo and re-echo through the courts of heaven. Will you be there?.
I want to praise Him; I want to honor Him that sitteth on the throne.
Your warfare is accomplished. Enter into the joy of thy Lord. Blessed, blessed benediction;
and then we can taste of the joys of the world to come."
God help us, and fill us with all fullness and power,
we shall soon hear the voice of the Saviour richer than any music, saying,
I want to hear it from His immortal lips.
